{"tid":16028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多倫多大學發現　即使中國用戶身處海外　微信仍會政治審查發言","createTime":"2016-12-01T09:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T10:21:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a88b9ff0e3293ec1485fbc252e4d468bf7c1b086","tid":16028,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/wechat-09_IF6QN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwechat-09_IF6QN_1200x0.png&h=e00587ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大多倫多大學一項研究發現，大陸科網公司騰訊的即時通訊 App微信（WeChat），針對大陸用戶及海外用戶，採用不同的審查準則，而大陸用戶身處海外時，審查會更加嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n多倫多大學 Citizen Lab近日發表研究〈一App兩制：微信在中國與境外採用不同審查機制〉（One App, Two Systems: How WeChat uses one censorship policy in China and another internationally）<br />\n<br />\n研究指出，對於以大陸電話號碼註冊的用戶，微信會對其進行敏感字審查，即使該用戶之後身處海外，或改用海外電話號碼，審查仍會繼續。而使用大陸以外地區，如香港、美國等地號碼註冊的用戶，則不會受到審查。<br />\n<br />\n研究亦指，過往，用戶在發言被屏蔽後，會收到訊息發送失敗的通知，但這項設定已悄然消失，用戶的發言若被屏敝，亦不會知道自己的發言事實上並無發出。<br />\n<br />\n多大測試亦發現，除了「西藏獨立」、「民主運動」等字眼，一些與中國維穩系統並無直接關係的事件，如伊斯蘭國危機也是微信會屏蔽的敏感詞，如「堅守科巴尼 敘利亞」，而一些與政治無關的字眼如「好萊塢艷照門種子」也會被屏蔽。另外，微信對群組討論的審查，比單對單對話更嚴格，群組討論的「敏感詞」數量比單對單對話更多。<br />\n<br />\n而一些敏感詞單獨發出時並不會被屏蔽，只在結合其他字眼時才無法發出，如「六四」可以發出，但「六四紀念館」不可以等。微信亦會屏蔽一些穆斯林的宗教字句。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=089cbf75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com&h=55c2db49\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com</a>"},{"pid":"a868c22b209c36edb24308ad245a959315779d25","tid":16028,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a9ab0c5a8bae5049e11cbb2ff78ed554695c58","tid":16028,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:02:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd4b18568e0fb2f12dda003321b9f8916155fa2","tid":16028,"uid":42452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"試諗下毒撚咁樣發幾條比女神<br />\n然後最重要果條被消失<br />\n女神冇回毒撚<br />\n毒撚以為女神冷落左佢<br />\n就此留下一世陰影"},{"pid":"737ffce2ea880683055b1cf0dbea1105a68495bd","tid":16028,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:11:47.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩審查"},{"pid":"15f8e044afb57509a8c19ca0816d9203783ca846","tid":16028,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你走都走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}